sql_query.sql: SELECT "accounts"."id" FROM "accounts" WHERE "accounts"."domain" IN (SELECT "instances"."domain" FROM "instances" WHERE (reverse('.' || domain) LIKE reverse('%.example.com'))) AND "accounts"."silenced_at" IS NULL ORDER BY "accounts"."id" ASC LIMIT $1

UPDATE "accounts" SET "silenced_at" = $1 WHERE "accounts"."domain" IN (SELECT "instances"."domain" FROM "instances" WHERE (reverse('.' || domain) LIKE reverse('%.example.com'))) AND "accounts"."silenced_at" IS NULL AND "accounts"."id" = $2

SELECT "accounts"."id" FROM "accounts" WHERE "accounts"."domain" IN (SELECT "instances"."domain" FROM "instances" WHERE (reverse('.' || domain) LIKE reverse('%.example.com'))) AND "accounts"."suspended_at" = $1 ORDER BY "accounts"."id" ASC LIMIT $2

UPDATE "accounts" SET "suspended_at" = $1, "suspension_origin" = $2 WHERE "accounts"."domain" IN (SELECT "instances"."domain" FROM "instances" WHERE (reverse('.' || domain) LIKE reverse('%.example.com'))) AND "accounts"."suspended_at" = $3 AND "accounts"."id" = $4
